==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wag-halter
<hw>Wag"-hal`ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Wag</ets> +
<ets>halter</ets>.]</ety> <def>One who moves or wears a halter; one
likely to be hanged.</def> <mark>[Colloq. & Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I can tell you, I am a mad <qex>wag-halter</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Marston.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wagnerian</ent>⟦br⟧
